02:17.338 --> 02:19.673
Night-night you two.

02:19.773 --> 02:21.242
Sweet dreams.

02:21.342 --> 02:22.443
Nighty night.

02:23.444 --> 02:26.447
(suspenseful music)

03:06.320 --> 03:08.856
(phone ringing)

03:12.025 --> 03:14.695
