03:14.795 --> 03:16.364
Oh, hi, Mr. Stroad.

03:17.465 --> 03:19.199
Yes, things are going great.

03:19.300 --> 03:22.670
I just put the little
troublemakers to bed.

03:24.672 --> 03:25.539
Oh my god.

03:27.741 --> 03:28.909
